title: PSG vs Internazionale - UEFA Champions League 2024/25 Final
description: This is the first ever competitive meeting between Inter and Paris SG. It’s also the second European Cup/UEFA Champions League final between an Italian and a French side, after Marseille beat Milan 1-0 in 1993 – the only time a French side has ever won the trophy. That final was also held in Munich. This is Inter’s seventh appearance in the European Cup/UEFA Champions League final, winning the trophy three times. They did lose their last final match, going down 1-0 against Manchester City in 2023.

title: DTM Show 2025 -Lausitzring
description: The DTM Show 2025 arrives at the DEKRA Lausitzring for Round 2 of the season, delivering high-speed drama on the 3.4 km circuit. With thrilling wins by Lucas Auer and Jack Aitken, the weekend showcased fierce GT3 competition. Support races from ADAC GT Masters and European Truck Racing added to an action-packed motorsport experience.

title: Feature Race - FIA Formula 3 Championship - Barcelona Round
description: The 2025 FIA Formula 3 Championship is an open-wheel racing category serving as the third tier of formula racing in the FIA Global Pathway. The category will be run in support of selected rounds of the 2025 FIA Formula One World Championship. As the championship is a spec series, all teams and drivers competing in the championship will run the same car, the Dallara F3 2025. Prema Racing are the reigning Teams Champions

title: Feature Race - FIA Formula 2 Championship - Barcelona Round
description: The 2025 FIA Formula 2 Championship is an open-wheel racing category serving as the second tier of formula racing in the FIA Global Pathway. The category will be run in support of selected rounds of the 2025 Formula One World Championship. As the championship is a spec series, all teams and drivers competing in the championship will run the same car, the new Dallara F2 2024. Invicta Racing are the reigning Teams Champions.

title: Race - Barcelona Round - Porsche SuperCup - 2025
description: Returns to the iconic Circuit de Barcelona-Catalunya for the third round of the 2025 season. After a five-year hiatus, the series makes its much-anticipated comeback to this challenging track, renowned for its blend of high-speed straights and technical corners. As part of the Formula 1 support program, the race showcases a grid of talented drivers competing in identical Porsche 911 GT3 Cup cars, ensuring close and competitive racing.

title: Main Race - F1 Spain Grand Prix - 2025
description: beIN SPORTS is the live and exclusive broadcast partners of Formula 1 until end of 2033 season. The 2025 Formula One season will feature 10 teams, 20 drivers, and a record 24 races across 21 countries, marking the championships 75th anniversary. All race weekends, including every Practice, Qualifying, Sprint and Race will be live and exclusive on beIN.

description: Covering everything from prototypes to endurance racing, karting to airplanes and even some real oddities… With both tradition and a fresh take on motorsport, Fast/Zone is the ultimate resource for everything that is fast and fascinating!

title: Match 1 / D9 - Simonne-Mathieu Court - Roland Garros - 2025
description: The 2025 Roland Garros is the 129th edition of the French Open overall. Within the Open Era, which began in 1968, the 2024 edition is the 58th edition. The event takes place from May 25 to June 8, 2025. This iconic clay-court championship features top players from around the world competing for glory in singles, doubles, and mixed doubles categories. As always, Roland Garros promises intense competition and unforgettable moments in the world of tennis.

title: The Outdoor Sports Show 2025
description: Welcome to this episode of Outdoor Sports Show, the TV magazine programme which takes you to the best events and introduces you to the characters from the action-packed world of outdoor sports. We strongly believe that from the many different paths we take in life, some of them must be dirt paths, because filling our lives with adventure gives us some great stories to share and this is what the outdoor sports show will bring to you!We now travel to the United Arab Emirates for another marathon. Staged under the auspices of the Dubai Sports Council, the Dubai Marathon celebrated its 24th anniversary with thousands of runners taking to the area around the iconic Burj Al Arab. title: Inside Sailing / 2025
description: Welcome to the 4th episode of Inside Sailing for 2025 - the TV program which brings you all the very best action from some of the most spectacular sailing events around the world. Through this epic sport we discover new horizons, new challenges, exciting journeys and some breathtaking sceneries.

title: World Sailing Show 2025
description: The World Sailing Show 2025 brings you the most thrilling moments from elite sailing competitions around the globe. From high-speed foiling action to tactical offshore battles, this episode covers top events like the America’s Cup, SailGP, and The Ocean Race. Meet the world’s best sailors, explore cutting-edge boat technology, and witness the drama of high-stakes racing on the water.

title: Nantes vs Cesson - LNH Division 1 - French Handball Starligue
description: Dive into the excitement of French handball with Liqui Moly Starligue, formerly LNH Division 1. Established in 1952, this premier league event features 16 top teams battling for glory. With Montpellier’s 14 Handball titles and Paris Saint-Germains 11 wins, the competition is fierce. Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.
